<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        /* CSS樣式 */
        .accordion {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #000000;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 18px;
            width: 100%;
            border: none;
            text-align: left;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: 0.4s;
            position: relative;
        }

            .accordion:hover, .accordion.active {
                color: white;
                background-color: #ffd33b;
            }

            .accordion::before {
                content: "";
                width: 10px;
                height: 10px;
                background-color: #ffd33b;
                border-radius: 50%;
                display: inline-block;
                position: absolute;
                left: -20px;
                top: 50%;
                transform: translateY(-50%);
            }

        .accordion-container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .panel {
            padding: 0 18px;
            display: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            color: #000000;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ffd33b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="accordion-container">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>

        <button class="accordion">What is the Sun made of?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>The Sun is primarily composed of hydrogen and helium gases.</p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">How far is the Moon from Earth?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>The average distance from Earth to the Moon is about 384,400 kilometers.</p>
        </div>

        <button class="accordion">What is the speed of light?</button>
        <div class="panel">
            <p>The speed of light in a vacuum is approximately 299,792 kilometers per second.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // JavaScript代碼
        var acc = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");
        var i;

        for (i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {
            acc[i].addEventListener("click", function () {
                this.classList.toggle("active");
                var panel = this.nextElementSibling;
                if (panel.style.display === "block") {
                    panel.style.display = "none";
                } else {
                    panel.style.display = "block";
                }
            });
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
